equals

public boolean equals(Step step)
This method compares two steps. Two Steps are said to be same in the following order
  • The passed Step's URL is not empty and current Step's URL is not empty and both of them matches. (Case Insensitive)
  • IF URL is empty for the current Step, the next element that is compared is, EnterText.If passed EnterText is not empty and current EnterText is not empty, a comparison is made.
  • If EnterText is empty, then next element that is compared is,LinkClick
  • If LinkClick is empty, then next element that is compared is,SelectOption
  • If SelectOption is empty, then next element that is compared is,SubmitAction
  • In All the cases, if any one of the elements matches in the order, a value of true is returned. Else false is returned

Parameters:
step - - Step to Compare
Returns:
boolean (Result of comparison of passed step with this Step)
